name: Stacy Sanders
text: It's a great place to see smart, beautiful & sexy college female students of all races.

name: Amanda Fox
text: Good old Campbell Hall. I've taken anatomy, anatomy lab, microbiology, microbiology lab, physiology lab, and psychology here. I have fond memories of napping on one of those big circular cushion chairs on the ground floor. It's probably one of the older buildings on campus but it serves its purpose. And it's not the humanities building, so it's got that going for it.
